------------------------------------------
  7/08  7/09  7/10  7/11  7/12  7/13  7/14
ğŸ§© Common Module â€“ coin_mapping.py
ğŸ“Œ What it does:
Maps user-friendly inputs like btc, eth to standard CoinGecko IDs like bitcoin, ethereum

Exports a function:

python
Copy
Edit
